    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was prescribed some antibiotics for this skin infection on my arm like 3 days ago. i've been taking them every day but honestly i feel totally fine now like the redness is gone and it doesnt even hurt anymore. is it okay if i just stop taking them now? i dont really want to keep putting chemicals in my body if i dont need to.",
